'''Ange Kagame''' ni umwana wa kabiri akaba n'umukobwa wenyine wa [[Paul Kagame]], perezida w'u [[Rwanda]] .  Yagize uruhare mu mpamvu zirimo kongerera ubushobozi abagore, uburezi, no kurandura ubukene, ndetse n'ubukangurambaga mugukingira imbaga nyamwinshi. Yashakanye na Bertrand Ndengeyingoma. <ref>Dec 29, 2018 Ange Kagame Engaged |url|=https://nairobinews.nation.co.ke/chillax/kagames-daughter-africas-hottest-spinster-off-the-market-photos/</ref>   bakaba bafitanye n'umwana w'umukobwa.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/entertainment/kagame-proud-grandpa-first-family-welcomes-first-grandchild</ref> 


== Ubuzima bwa mbere nu burere ==
Kagame yavutse ku ya 8 Nzeri 1993 i Buruseli mu [[Ububiligi|Bubiligi]] .  Se ni Paul Kagame, [[Perezida wa Repubulika y’u Rwanda|Perezida wa]] gatandatu [[Perezida wa Repubulika y’u Rwanda|wa Repubulika y'u Rwanda]] kandi akaba n'umuyobozi w'ishyaka rikomeye [[Ishyaka FPR-Inkotanyi|ry’u Rwanda rishinzwe gukunda igihugu FPR]] . Nyina Jeannette Nyiramongi n'umudamu wa mbere wa nyakubahwa Perezida wa Repubulika yu [[Rwanda]] .  Nk'umukobwa wa mbere wa perezida, afite imbaraga  zidasanzwe mu guhindura byinshi. 

Ange Kagame yarangije amashuri ye mu mahanga kandi ntiyigeze aboneka mu ruhame kuva mu ubwana bwe bwose kubera umutekano ndetse nubuzima bwe bwite  Yize mu ishuri rya Dana Hall, ishuri ryigenga  riherereye i Wellesley, muri Massachusetts muri Amerika. Yize muri Smith College aho yize ibijyanye na siyanse ya politiki hamwe n’ubumenyi  kuri Afurika. Afite kandi Masters mubigendanye ni bibazo mpuzamahanga yakuye muri kaminuza ya Columbia   Ange Kagame ashobora kuvuga indimi eshatu, Icyongereza, [[Ikinyarwanda|Kinyarwanda]], n'Igifaransa. 
[[File:President_Barack_Obama_and_First_Lady_Michelle_Obama_greet_His_Excellency_Paul_Kagame,_President_of_the_Republic_of_Rwanda,_and_his_daughter.jpg|thumb|Ange Kagame (second from right) with President [[Barack Obama]] (left), His Excellency [[Paul Kagame]], President of the Republic of Rwanda (second from left), and First Lady Michelle Obama (right).]]
Muri 2014, Ange Kagame yaherekeje se muri [[Perezidansi y’Amerika|White House]] gusangira na [[Barack Obama|Perezida Barack Obama]] .  Iri funguro ryari mu nama y’iminsi itatu y’abayobozi b’Amerika - Afurika y’abayobozi yateranye muri Kanama uwo mwaka,  aho abayobozi b’ibihugu byinshi bya Afurika bahuriye kugira ngo baganire ku bucuruzi, ishoramari n’umutekano by’umugabane.  <ref>Dec 30, 2015 Ange Kagame speaks of forgiveness |url|=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2LIjZDt-tUU</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Kagame ni umwana wa kabiri mukuru ufite abandi bavandimwe batatu, [[Ivan Cyomoro]], [[Ian Kagame]], na [[Brian Kagame]].  Numufana wa [[Umupira w’agatebo|basketball]] [[Umupira w’amaguru|n'umupira wamaguru]], akurikirana cyane Boston Celtics na Arsenal . Ku ya 6 Nyakanga 2019, mu kigo cyitwa Intare Conference Center i Kigali, Ange yashakanye na Bertrand Ndengeyingoma bakaba bafitanye n'umwana w'umukobwa.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/entertainment/kagame-proud-grandpa-first-family-welcomes-first-grandchild</ref> 

